---
description: Thin HTTP handlers — validate, call use case, map errors once
globs: "**/*.{controller,route,routes,handler}.{ts,js}"
alwaysApply: false
---

# HTTP handlers (ADAPT)

- Validate input at the boundary
- No ORM calls inside controllers
- Pass plain objects into use cases — not `req`/`res`
- Delegate error mapping to central filter/middleware
- Document status codes and error `code`s for new endpoints
